    <item>
      <title>独家：非洲国家考虑全球首个“债务换自然”联合项目</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/african-countries-eye-worlds-first-joint-debt-for-nature-swap-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一家全球保护组织称，至少有五个非洲国家正在进行可能是世界上第一个联合“债务换自然”项目，旨在筹集至少 20 亿美元用于保护珊瑚丰富的印度洋海域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/african-countries-eye-worlds-first-joint-debt-for-nature-swap-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 15:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据彭博社报道，富国银行向美联储提交了关于取消资产上限的重要审查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargo-sends-fed-crucial-review-lifting-asset-cap-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻周四援引知情人士的话称，富国银行已向美联储提交了一份关于其风险和控制改革的第三方评估报告，以寻求取消监管机构施加的资产上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/wells-fargo-sends-fed-crucial-review-lifting-asset-cap-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 14:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将在新检查中调查银行交易对手风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ecb-will-look-into-banks-counterparty-risk-new-check-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行监督员克劳迪娅·布赫周四表示，欧洲央行将在明年进行的新一轮健康检查中，调查银行对基金等其他金融公司的风险敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ecb-will-look-into-banks-counterparty-risk-new-check-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 14:09:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼表示贴现窗口的使用是为了紧急情况</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-says-discount-window-use-is-emergencies-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔鲍曼周四表示，银行使用美联储贴现窗口是为了应急，而不是为了满足更常见的流动性需求，这种狭隘的观点似乎与银行监管机构近期推动银行更积极地使用该工具的做法形成了鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/feds-bowman-says-discount-window-use-is-emergencies-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 14:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利副总理在德国商业银行交易中提出裕信银行的法律基础问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italy-deputy-pm-would-not-like-unicredit-shift-legal-base-germany-commerzbank-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利副总理马泰奥·萨尔维尼周四表示，他不希望裕信银行在与德国商业银行达成的交易中将其法律基地转移到德国，且罗马方面仍在考虑其对合并的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italy-deputy-pm-would-not-like-unicredit-shift-legal-base-germany-commerzbank-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 13:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗与阿波罗合作推出 250 亿美元私人信贷计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/citi-apollo-partner-25-bln-private-credit-deals-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团和阿波罗全球合作开展一项 250 亿美元的私人信贷和直接贷款计划，这表明银行和非银行之间的联盟日益加强，希望在利润丰厚的 2 万亿美元市场中分一杯羹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/citi-apollo-partner-25-bln-private-credit-deals-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:56:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西银行发起活动遏制农业企业破产</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banco-do-brasil-launches-campaign-curb-agribusiness-bankruptcies-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国有银行巴西银行（按资产计算为巴西第二大银行）一位高管周三表示，该银行于 6 月份发起了一项活动，以应对农业综合企业领域破产申请数量的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banco-do-brasil-launches-campaign-curb-agribusiness-bankruptcies-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:54:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
