      <title>高盛表示，专注于中国的对冲基金业绩受刺激而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-china-focused-hedge-fund-performance-juiced-by-stimulus-says-goldman-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛经纪公司的一份报告显示，在中国央行推出自 2020 年新冠疫情以来最大规模刺激措施后，交易中国股票的对冲基金本周出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-china-focused-hedge-fund-performance-juiced-by-stimulus-says-goldman-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦呼吁警惕金融稳定，警告不要放松监管</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-call-more-financial-stability-work-thoughtful-regulation-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦周四呼吁继续努力确保金融体系具有韧性，包括推行深思熟虑的监管并反击那些想要降低银行资本要求的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-call-more-financial-stability-work-thoughtful-regulation-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:34:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团和忠利集团联手为法国散户投资者打造私募债务基金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackstone-generali-team-up-private-debt-fund-french-retail-investors-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石集团和意大利最大保险公司忠利集团周四在声明中表示，两家公司将联手成立一只基金，允许法国散户投资者投资私人公司债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackstone-generali-team-up-private-debt-fund-french-retail-investors-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对权力的渴求使 ESG 投资者对科技股的热爱变得复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/power-thirst-complicates-esg-investors-love-affair-with-tech-stocks-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者表示，管理着数千亿美元资金的投资者正在敦促微软、 Alphabet 和其他公司提供有关人工智能和高级计算所需能力的更多信息，以帮助决定该行业是否应该在可持续基金中保持较高比例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/power-thirst-complicates-esg-investors-love-affair-with-tech-stocks-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法官对纽约针对特朗普的民事欺诈案表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-ask-new-york-appeals-court-toss-nearly-500-mln-civil-fraud-judgment-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，上诉法院法官对纽约州对唐纳德·特朗普提起的民事欺诈案表示怀疑，因为这位前总统要求他们撤销一项针对特朗普的近五亿美元的判决，因为一名审判法官宣布特朗普的房地产商业行为存在欺诈行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-ask-new-york-appeals-court-toss-nearly-500-mln-civil-fraud-judgment-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
